---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Projetos · edu.dev">
  <h1>Projetos</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-10">Coisas que construí ou estou construindo.</p>

  <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
    <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-site-surface-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark rounded-lg">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold border-none pb-0 mt-0"><a href="https://github.com/JoKenPo/notionfly-iii" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-brand">notionfly-iii</a></h2>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium whitespace-nowrap"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg> 5</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">🔥🦟 Aplicativo de controle financeiro inspirado no Firefly III, utilizando o Notion como banco de dados.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">React Native</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Expo</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Notion API</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-site-surface-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark rounded-lg">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold border-none pb-0 mt-0"><a href="https://github.com/JoKenPo/fakerepo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-brand">fakerepo</a></h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Arquitetura de monorepo escalável para gerenciamento de múltiplos pacotes e aplicações integradas.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Monorepo</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Lerna / Turborepo</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-site-surface-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark rounded-lg">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold border-none pb-0 mt-0"><a href="https://github.com/JoKenPo/site" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="no-underline text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-brand">site (jokenpo.dev)</a></h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Código-fonte aberto deste próprio site pessoal, construído focado em performance pura com Astro e estilização com Tailwind CSS.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Astro</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Tailwind CSS</span>
        <span class="bg-white dark:bg-site-bg-dark border border-gray-200 dark:border-site-border-dark px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Self-hosted</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
